::Zardus/Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Zardus chucles as he sees Soundwave go into statis lock. He walks to the 
door, the blast doors opening and autoguns ceasing fire.

"He's in your hands," Zardus says to Nemesis Enforcer, "Do whatever you want 
with him. I have a new soldier to reprogram."

Zardus walks out of the door, heading for the lab.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica and DevilDuer finish strapping Feline to the lab table. They step 
back, looking at the female.

"I hope Zardus will program her to be really hot," DevilDuer says, grinning.

"Really? So that she'd totaly ignore you?"

DevilDuer growls at this comment from Reptilica. "Oh shut up," he mutters, 
waiting for Zardus get there.
